test_name: DSORTOT compared to DSPRSINF and DSSEASDY
short_desc: DSORTOT must equal the sum of DSPRSINF and DSSEASDY if both have valid scores
full_desc: Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 Total score) must equal the sum of Q1a1. DSPRSINF (Personal information) and Q1b1. DSSEASDY (Season/Day) if If Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSPRSINF ne  8 (N/A) and DSSEADY ne 8 (N/A)
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSPRSINF ne 8  and DSSEASDY ne 8 AND DSORTOT ne DSPRSINF + DSSEASDY

test_name: DSSMTOT compared to DSSMIMM and DSSMDEL
short_desc: DSSMTOT must equal the sum of DSSMIMM and DSSMDEL if both have valid scores
full_desc: Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score) must equal the sum of Q1c1. DSSMIMM (Shoebox memory - Immediate) and Q1c2. DSSMDEL (Shoebox memory - delayed) if Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSSMIMM ne 88 (N/A)  and DSSMDEL ne 88 (N/A)
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSSMIMM ne 88 or DSSMDEL ne 88 AND DSSMTOT ne DSSMIMM + DSSMDEL

test_name: DSMMTOT compared to DSMEMIMM and DSMEMDEL
short_desc: DSMMTOT must equal the sum of DSMEMIMM and DSMEMDEL if both have valid scores
full_desc: Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score) must equal the sum of Q1d1. DSMEMIMM (Memory - Immediate) and Q1d2. DSMEMDEL (Memory - Delay) if Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSMEMIMM ne 8 (N/A) and DSMEMDEL ne 8 (N/A)
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSMEMIMM ne 8 and DSMEMDEL ne 8 AND DSMMTOT ne DSMEMIMM + DSMEMDEL

test_name: DSAPTOT compared to DSAPINT and DSAPTRAN
short_desc: DSAPTOT must equal the sum of DSAPINT and DSAPTRAN if both have valid scores
full_desc: Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - total score) must equal the sum of Q1e1. DSAPINT (Apraxia - intransitive) and Q1e2. DSAPTRAN (Apraxia - transitive) if Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSAPINT ne 8 (N/A) and DSAPTRAN ne 8.8 (N/A)
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSAPINT ne 8 and DSAPTRAN ne 8.8 AND DSAPTOT ne DSAPINT + DSAPTRAN

test_name: DSLGTOT compared to DSLGNAM, DSLGREP, DSLGCOMP
short_desc: DSLGTOT must equal the sum of DSLGNAM, DSLGREP and DSLGCOMP if all subtests have valid scores
full_desc: Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - total score) must equal the sum of Q1f1. DSLGNAM (Language - Naming), Q1f2. DSLGREP (Language - repetitions) and Q1f3. DSLGCOMP (Language - comprehension) if Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSLGNAM ne 88 (N/A) and DSLGREP ne 88 (N/A) and DSLGCOMP ne 88.8 (N/A)
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSLGNAM ne 88 and DSLGREP ne 88 and DSLGCOMP ne 88.8 AND DSLGTOT ne DSLGNAM + DSLGREP + DSLGCOMP

test_name: DSMSETT compared to DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT and DSKNWTT
short_desc: DSMSETT must equal the sum of DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT and DSKNWTT if all subtotals have valid scores
full_desc: Q1i1. DSMSETT (DSMSE Total score) must equal the sum of Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 total Score), Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score), Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score), Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - Total score), Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - Total score), Q1g2. DSVISTT (Visuospatial - Total score) and Q1h2. DSKNWTT (Knowledge of the examiner - Total score) if Q1. DSMSEADM (Any part of DSMSE administered?) = 1 (Yes) and DSORTOT ne 88 and DSSMTOT ne 88 and DSMMTOT ne 8 and DSAPTOT ne 8.8 and DSLGTOT ne 88.8 and DSVISTT ne 8.8 and DSKNWTT ne 8
test_logic: If DSMSEADM=1 and DSORTOT ne 88 and DSSMTOT ne 88 and DSMMTOT ne 8 and DSAPTOT ne 8.8 and DSLGTOT ne 88.8 and DSVISTT ne 8.8 and DSKNWTT ne 8 and DSMSETT ne (DSORTOT + DSSMTOT + DSMMTOT + DSAPTOT + DSLGTOT + DSVISTT + DSKNWTT)
comp_vars: DSMSEADM, DSMSETT, DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT, DSKNWTT

test_name: DSCRTTFR compared to DSCRT1FR, DSCRT2FR, DSCRT3FR
short_desc: DSCRTTFR must equal the sum of DSCRT1FR, DSCRT2FR, DSCRT3FR
full_desc: Q2d13. DSCRTTFR (Free recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d1. DSCRT1FR (Test trial - Trial 1, free recall), Q2d5. DSCRT2FR (Test trial - Trial 2, free recall), Q2d9. DSCRT3FR (Test trial - Trial 3, free recall) if Q2a. DSCRADM (Any part of the Cued Recall Task administered?) = 1 (Yes)
test_logic: If DSCRADM =1 and DSCRTTFR ne DSCRT1FR + DSCRT2FR + DSCRT3FR

test_name: DSCRTTIF compared to DSCRT1IF, DSCRT2IF, DSCRT3IF
short_desc: DSCRTTIF must equal the sum of DSCRT1IF, DSCRT2IF, DSCRT3IF
full_desc: Q2d14. DSCRTTIF (Intrusions to free recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d2. DSCRT1IF (Test trial - Trial 1, intrusions to free recall), Q2d6. DSCRT2IF (Test trial - Trial 2, intrusions to free recall), Q2d10. DSCRT3IF (Test trial - Trial 3, intrusions to free recall) if Q2a. DSCRADM (Any part of the Cued Recall Task administered?) = 1 (Yes)
test_logic: If DSCRADM =1 and DSCRTTIF ne DSCRT1IF + DSCRT2IF + DSCRT3IF

test_name: DSCRTTCR compared to DSCRT1CR, DSCRT2CR, DSCRT3CR
short_desc: DSCRTTCR must equal the sum of DSCRT1CR, DSCRT2CR, DSCRT3CR
full_desc: Q2d15. DSCRTTCR (Cued recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d3. DSCRT1CR (Test trial - Trial 1, cued recall), Q2d7. DSCRT2CR (Test trial - Trial 2, cued recall), Q2d11. DSCRT3CR (Test trial - Trial 3, cued recall) if Q2a. DSCRADM (Any part of the Cued Recall Task administered?) = 1 (Yes)
test_logic: If DSCRADM =1 and DSCRTTCR ne DSCRT1CR + DSCRT2CR + DSCRT3CR

test_name: DSCRTTIC compared to DSCRT1IC, DSCRT2IC, DSCRT3IC
short_desc: DSCRTTIC must equal the sum of DSCRT1IC, DSCRT2IC, DSCRT3IC
full_desc: Q2d16. DSCRTTIC (Intrusions to cued recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d4. DSCRT1IC (Test trial - Trial 1, intrusions to cued recall), Q2d8. DSCRT2IC (Test trial - Trial 2, intrusions to cued recall), Q2d12. DSCRT3IC (Test trial - Trial 3, intrusions to cued recall) if Q2a. DSCRADM (Any part of the Cued Recall Task administered?) = 1 (Yes)
test_logic: If DSCRADM =1 and DSCRTTIC ne DSCRT1IC + DSCRT2IC + DSCRT3IC

test_name: DSORTOT compared to DSPRSINF and DSSEASDY
short_desc: DSORTOT must = 88 if DSPRSINF = 8 or DSSEASDY = 8
full_desc: Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 Total score) must be 88 (N/A) if Q1a1. DSPRSINF (Personal information) = 8 (N/A) or Q1b1. DSSEASDY (Season/Day) = 8 (N/A)
test_logic: If (DSSEASDY = 8 or  DSPRSINF = 8) AND DSORTOT ne 88

test_name: DSSMTOT compared to DSSMIMM and DSSMDEL
short_desc: DSSMTOT must = 88 if DSSMIMM = 88 or DSSMDEL = 88
full_desc: Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score) must be 88 (N/A) if Q1c1. DSSMIMM (Shoebox memory - Immediate) = 88 (N/A) or Q1c2. DSSMDEL (Shoebox memory - delayed) if DSSMIMM = 88 (N/A)
test_logic: If (DSSMIMM = 88 or DSSMDEL = 88) AND DSSMTOT ne 88

test_name: DSMMTOT compared to DSMEMIMM and DSMEMDEL
short_desc: DSMMTOT must = 8 if DSMEMIMM = 8 or DSMEMDEL = 8
full_desc: Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score) must equal 8 (N/A) if Q1d1. DSMEMIMM (Memory - Immediate)  = 8 (N/A) or Q1d2. DSMEMDEL (Memory - Delay) = 8 (N/A)
test_logic: If (DSMEMIMM = 8  or DSMEMDEL = 8) AND DSMMTOT ne 8

test_name: DSAPTOT compared to DSAPINT and DSAPTRAN
short_desc: DSAPTOT must = 8.8 if DSAPINT = 8 or DSAPTRAN = 8.8
full_desc: Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - total score) must equal 8.8 (N/A) if Q1e1. DSAPINT (Apraxia - intransitive) = 8 (N/A) or Q1e2. DSAPTRAN (Apraxia - transitive) = 8.8 (N/A)
test_logic: If (DSAPINT = 8 or DSAPTRAN = 8.8) AND DSAPTOT ne 8.8

test_name: DSLGTOT compared to DSLGNAM, DSLGREP, DSLGCOMP
short_desc: DSLGTOT must = 88.8 (N/A) if any subtest has invalid/missing scores (DSLGNAM = 88 OR DSLGREP = 88 OR DSLGCOMP = 88.8)
full_desc: Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - total score) must equal 88.8 (N/A) if Q1f1. DSLGNAM (Language - Naming) = 88 (N/A) or Q1f2. DSLGREP (Language - repetitions) = 88 (N/A) or Q1f3. DSLGCOMP (Language - comprehension) = 88.8 (N/A)
test_logic: If (DSLGNAM = 88 or DSLGREP = 88 or DSLGCOMP = 88.8) AND DSLGTOT ne 88.8

test_name: DSMSETT compared to DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT and DSKNWTT
short_desc: DSMSETT must equal 995.0, 996.0, 997.0, or 998.0 if DSORTOT=88 or DSSMTOT=88 or DSMMTOT =8 or DSAPTOT = 8.8 or DSLGTOT = 88.8 or DSVISTT = 8.8 or DSKNWTT =8
full_desc: Q1i1. DSMSETT (DSMSE Total score) must equal 995.0, 996.0, 997.0, or 998.0 (not completed) if Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 total Score) = 88 or Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score) = 88 or Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score) = 8 or Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - Total score) = 8.8 or Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - Total score) = 88.8 or Q1g2. DSVISTT (Visuospatial - Total score) = 8.8 or Q1h2. DSKNWTT (Knowledge of the examiner - Total score) =8
test_logic: If (DSORTOT=88 or DSSMTOT=88 or DSMMTOT =8 or DSAPTOT = 8.8 or DSLGTOT = 88.8 or DSVISTT = 8.8 or DSKNWTT =8) and DSMSETT not in (995.0, 996.0, 997.0, 998.0)
comp_vars: DSMSETT, DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT, DSKNWTT

full_desc: Q1g2. DSVISTT  (Visuospatial - Total score)  must equal Q1g1. DSVISUO (Visuospatial)
Q1h2. DSKNWTT  (Knowledge of examiner - Total score)  must equal Q1h1. DSKNOWL (Knowledge of examiner)
